CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 8, 1964, pg. 1 reads: "Choral Group - Shown above are a few members of the choral group of fourth, fifth and sixth grade members at Miller School. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of choral group with twelve girls from fourth, fifth, and sixth grades, posed on stage at Miller Elementary School
